{
  "stem": "4753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wanted to mention to you that during my time in concentration camp and so on, my opinion about the German was horrible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they were unbelievable, the atrocities what they were capable to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I wanted to tell you between the German people were also some decent people-- not many, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because if that would have been many, that wouldn't have happened what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that goes for the Hungarians also-- my beloved Hungarians, you know, whom I trusted so much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was ready to give my life for Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were many, many, many of them, most of them, who were pointing out the homes of the Jews and didn't offer any help.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we did go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had two workers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, he had four, but two who came to our door and said we should give everything what we have to them, because we will be killed anyway.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and they were Hungarians that worked for my father many, many, many years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents helped them with everything beside their paycheck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was happening to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was unbelievable, we still tried to deny why things happening the way happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the ghetto, the SS men one day came in and said we have 10 minutes to pack together everything what we want to take.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we will be relocated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are going to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So whatever we could grab, we did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We did go middle of the road in the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my beloved Hungarians were lined in the sidewalks looking at us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many people asked for water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because between us were all the people, sick people, kicked out from the hospital because they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
